INSERT INTO
                factory_deps (
                    bytecode_hash,
                    bytecode,
                    miniblock_number,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            SELECT
                u.bytecode_hash,
                u.bytecode,
                $3,
                NOW(),
                NOW()
            FROM
                UNNEST($1 :: bytea [], $2 :: bytea []) AS u (bytecode_hash, bytecode) ON CONFLICT (bytecode_hash) DO NOTHING
